AppIfElseTests

This class contains unit tests for the AppIf and AppElse functionality in the ASE Application Demo. Tests ensure that the conditional logic of the AppIf and AppElse commands are executed correctly under different scenarios with no restriction errors.

AppIntTests

This class contains unit tests for the AppInt class functionality in the ASE Application Demo. Tests validate basic assignments, expression calculations, and restrictions of integer operations.

AppMethodTests

This class contains unit tests for the AppMethod functionality in the ASE Application Demo. The tests verify correct parsing, method declaration, and handling of method execution errors.

AppWhileTests

This class contains unit tests for the AppWhile class functionality in the ASE Application Demo. It validates that while loops execute correctly and handle multiple iterations without errors.
